comment: Sweet, little spice like cinnamon and a nice pleasant finish that reminds me of mint. Great value-I’ll be buying another when this is out.

Good, sweet, light, TX whiskey.  No real mid drink rye bite but a mellow transition to a light finish into that 90 proof heat.  Does not hold up to water.  Drink it straight.  Perfect daily drinker.  Decent bang 4 the bucks here.
A potent whiskey with a buck ton of flavor
I'm still new to drinking whiskey but to me this is something I would drink on a regular and would buy again
